       bbrreeaakk           4   In fill mode, lines which could not  be  broken  so
                           that  their  length  was less than the line length.
                           This is enabled by default.

       cchhaarr            1   Non-existent  characters.   This  is   enabled   by
                           default.

       ccoolloorr      524288   Color-related warnings.

